2013-03-22  Stephan Bosch  <stephan@rename-it.nl>

	* configure.ac, src/lib-sievestorage/Makefile.am, src/lib-sievestorage
	/sieve-storage.c, src/lib-sievestorage/sieve-storage.h,
	src/managesieve/Makefile.am, src/plugins/Makefile.am, src/plugins
	/doveadm-sieve/Makefile.am, src/plugins/doveadm-sieve/doveadm-sieve-
	plugin.c:
	Committed Timo's patch that adds a plugin that provides Sieve dsync
	support. http://dovecot.org/patches/2.2/doveadm-sieve-plugin.diff
	Made some small modifications. This code should not interfere with
	normal ManageSieve operation, so I commit this right now without
	much testing. The actual doveadm sieve plugin has a few open issues
	that need to be resolved still.
	[43b09b9a2f72]

2013-03-04  Stephan Bosch  <stephan@rename-it.nl>

	* src/lib-sieve/sieve-actions.c:
	lib-sieve: Fixed segfault bug in reject. Passed senv->script_context
	rather than senv itself. Somehow the compiler fails to warn about
	this.
	[b75b00760b86]

