	inadequate because an error was still logged.
	[5c1ce25596ed]

	* src/lib-sieve/sieve-actions.c:
	lib-sieve: fileinto/keep: don't log quota errors to syslog but
	rather to user's log. Prevents administrator frustration about
	useless log messages caused by users with too much mail.
	[7301a7ed8800]

