2012-08-29  Stephan Bosch  <stephan@rename-it.nl>

	* src/lib-sieve/edit-mail.c:
	lib-sieve: fixed edit-mail istream to work with latest Dovecot.
	Testsuite failed with an assertion, because the stream returned -2
	at an unexpected time. I've restructured the buffering
	implementation to prevent this. The testsuite succeeds now, but this
	needs to be tested more thoroughly.
	[061d4993b509]

