2012-05-20  Stephan Bosch  <stephan@rename-it.nl>

	* configure.in, doc/editheader.txt, doc/include.txt, doc/spamtest-
	virustest.txt, doc/vacation.txt, src/lib-sieve-tool/mail-raw.c, src
	/lib-sieve/cmd-redirect.c, src/lib-sieve/edit-mail.c, src/lib-
	sieve/plugins/body/ext-body-common.c, src/lib-sieve/sieve-smtp.c,
