	* src/lib-managesieve/managesieve-parser.c, src/managesieve-login
	/client-authenticate.c, src/managesieve/cmd-putscript.c:
	lib-managesieve: changed EPROTO error to EIO in ManageSieve string
	stream because it is apparently not known in BSD.
	[ef5045159e6b]

