	a stream. Fixes support for handing large SASL responses. Also
	resolves long-standing FIXME regarding the second parameter of
	PUTSCRIPT: it can now be a quoted string. Includes a few small
	changes in the login daemon that were done in the dovecot
	equivalents before.
	[ae857042882b]

