	* INSTALL, README, doc/example-config/conf.d/90-sieve.conf,
	src/plugins/lda-sieve/lda-sieve-plugin.c:
	LDA Sieve plugin: renamed sieve_global_path setting to sieve_default
	for clarity. Old name is now deprecated. Support for the even older
	global_script_path name for this setting is dropped.
	[bd5cffe2ed95]

	* INSTALL, doc/example-config/conf.d/90-sieve.conf, src/lib-sieve/cmd-
	redirect.c:
	lib-sieve: added means to prohibit use of redirect action. Setting
	sieve_max_redirects=0 now means that redirects are prohibited rather
	than unlimited. Now there is always a limit, but it can be enormous
	if the administrator wants to.
	[83fc2f6edefa]

