	[81389f35d988]

	* src/lib-sieve/plugins/spamvirustest/ext-spamvirustest-common.c:
	Spamtest extension: fixed small bug in yesno-type spam header
	matching.
	[cfe04d40b164]

	* src/testsuite/testsuite-settings.c:
