	/lib-sieve/tst-exists.c, src/lib-sieve/tst-header.c, src/lib-sieve
	/tst-not.c, src/lib-sieve/tst-size.c:
	Implemented support for overriding default argument implementations
	of number, string and string-list.
	[811636f212aa]

